## raw 110 — systematic ablation, causal core
@r110_raw_id raw_110_systematic_ablation_causal_core
@r110_raw_concept N-component system → enumerate all 2^N - 1 non-empty subsets, measure Φ on each, isolate component(s) whose removal causes >X% Φ-drop. Causal core = minimal subset that preserves ≥(1-ε)·Φ_full.
@r110_anima_landing_primary /Users/ghost/core/anima/verifier/  # NEW candidate file: ablation_causal_core.hexa — orchestrate measure_all_engines.hexa repeatedly with each engine ablated, identify causal-core engine subset.
@r110_anima_landing_secondary /Users/ghost/core/anima/anima-measurement/measure_all_engines.hexa  # extend with --ablate <engine_slug,...> CLI flag enabling subset-measurement loop.
@r110_minimal_reproducer_pointer anima-measurement/measure_all_engines.hexa — currently measures all engines unconditionally; add ablate-loop driver above.
@r110_tracking_id anima/convergence/issues/TBD-r110-systematic-ablation-driver
